<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:nāgarī maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>sadattā dasu gunaṁ pūnaṁ
<lb n="2"/>paradattā nu pālaṇe [<g type="danda">.</g>]
<lb n="3"/>paradattā <unclear>Etha</unclear> pahāreṇa(ḥ)
<lb n="4"/>sadattā nisphalaṁ bhavet [<g type="ddanda">.</g>]
<lb n="5"/>vīraśrī gajapati gauḍesvara navakoṭi karnāṭa kalavarakesvara vīrapratāpa
<lb n="6"/>śrīmukunda deu māhārājāṁ ṅkara vije [<g type="danda">.</g>] subharāije samasta 8 śarke
<lb n="7"/>śrīnarasiṅghanātha devaṅkū bhāta bhogakū bhiāki jīara deulara
<lb n="8"/>prakaṇāṇḍa kalā—ṭa 1255 kā Amṛtakuṇḍakū ṭa 385 kā cīṭākū ṭa 190 kā
<lb n="9"/>gāe ṭa 525 <unclear>tri</unclear>thilā [<g type="danda">.</g>] kaliṅgadaṇḍapāṭhara jāara Anakāpali peṭa Adhipa
<lb n="10"/>sahasradhā Adhiṣṭhāna kari (vighi) ṭa 525 kā [<g type="danda">.</g>] E rakāṅka <unclear>yilṛ</unclear> kesikṣādā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ri <g type="danda">.</g> <unclear>kebhi</unclear> Ācandramārka gomuṇāpo <unclear>karathila</unclear> [<g type="danda">.</g>] caratana ṭa 150 kā kathilājā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ara dasa paṁ ṭa 150 ṅkā harirāja <unclear>daviḍa</unclear> māhāpātraṅka <unclear>tho</unclear> ṭīkū tala jaarasū
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṭā [<g type="danda">.</g>] <unclear>A</unclear>harniśamū dhūpāki grāma [<g type="danda">.</g>] dharmaki ratimāna je <unclear>hūi</unclear> sedosad<unclear>ā</unclear>ri
<lb n="14"/>Amṛta moṇoi bhittara visa delo pateka pāi
</p>

